HEADWORD: Billon
<hw>Bil`lon"</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F. Cf.
<er>Billet</er> a stick.]</ety> <def>An alloy of gold and silver with a
large proportion of copper or other base metal, used in
coinage.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

